The main.css file, replace to the main web page one by one: 

p.one {
    position: absolute; left: 30px; top: 30px;
    border: 4px solid #c0c0c0;
    padding: 10px;
}

p.one {
    position: relative; left: 30px; top: 30px;
    border: 4px solid #c0c0c0;
    padding: 10px;
}

p.one {
    position: fixed; left: 30px; top: 30px;
    border: 4px solid #c0c0c0;
    padding: 10px;
}

The main web page, with main.css file attached:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Positioning Application</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="main.css">
    </head
    <body>
        <h3>CSS Positioning Application</h3>
        <p class="one">Hello YouTubers, welcome to software developer channel. Learn programming for free.</p>
    </body>
</html>
